{"prompt": "Develop an engaging platform for a virtual book club. The primary color should be a deep wine red.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Virtual Book Club</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #800020; /* Deep Wine Red */\n            color: #f0e6e6; /* Light Off-White for contrast */\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #800020; /* Deep Wine Red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); /* Subtle translucent background */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #f0e6e6;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #a05252; /* Slightly lighter wine red */\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n        }\n        .book-list, .discussion-forum, .events {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n        .book-item, .forum-post, .event-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);\n            padding: 1rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #a05252; /* Slightly lighter wine red */\n        }\n        .book-item h3, .forum-post h3, .event-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #f0e6e6;\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n        }\n        .book-item p, .forum-post p, .event-item p {\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #a05252; /* Slightly lighter wine red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #800020; /* Deep Wine Red */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            background-color: #800020; /* Deep Wine Red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>The Crimson Quill Book Club</h1>\n        <p>Dive into stories, share insights, and connect with fellow readers.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"current-book\">\n            <h2>Currently Reading</h2>\n            <div class=\"book-item\">\n                <h3>\"The Midnight Library\"</h3>\n                <p>Author: Matt Haig</p>\n                <p>Discussion Date: October 28th, 2023</p>\n                <p>Join the discussion on our <a href=\"#discussion\" style=\"color: #f0e68c;\">forum</a>!</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"book-list\">\n            <h2>Past Reads</h2>\n            <div class=\"book-item\">\n                <h3>\"Project Hail Mary\"</h3>\n                <p>Author: Andy Weir</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"book-item\">\n                <h3>\"Where the Crawdads Sing\"</h3>\n                <p>Author: Delia Owens</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"discussion-forum\" id=\"discussion\">\n            <h2>Discussion Forum</h2>\n            <div class=\"forum-post\">\n                <h3>Thoughts on Chapter 5?</h3>\n                <p>Posted by: Alex R. - 2 days ago</p>\n                <p>I found the parallel narratives really engaging here. What did everyone else think about the ending of the chapter?</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"forum-post\">\n                <h3>Character Analysis: Nora Seed</h3>\n                <p>Posted by: Sarah K. - 5 days ago</p>\n                <p>Let's talk about Nora's journey. Do you relate to her struggles? What are your predictions for her future?</p>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Join the Discussion</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"events\">\n            <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>\n            <div class=\"event-item\">\n                <h3>Virtual Author Q&A</h3>\n                <p>Date: November 15th, 2023</p>\n                <p>Details: Live Q&A session with [Guest Author Name]. Submit your questions in advance!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"event-item\">\n                <h3>Monthly Book Selection Poll</h3>\n                <p>Date: November 1st, 2023</p>\n                <p>Help us choose next month's read! Vote for your favorite from the nominated titles.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"join-us\">\n            <h2>Join Our Community</h2>\n            <p>Ready to embark on new literary adventures with us? Sign up today!</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Sign Up Now</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 The Crimson Quill Book Club. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add subtle JavaScript for future interactivity, e.g., smooth scrolling\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}